Cargo Hero Section
A simple, responsive hero section for a cargo company's website, built with HTML and CSS. This project showcases a visually appealing landing page element featuring a cargo truck background image, headline, subtext, and a call-to-action button.

Features
Responsive Design: Adapts to different screen sizes for mobile and desktop viewing.
Customizable: Easily modify text, colors, and images to fit your brand.
Free Hosting: Hosted live on GitHub Pages for easy sharing.

Background Image: The current image is from Unsplash (free to use). For a custom image, ensure it's high-resolution and cargo-themed.
Styling: Modify the <style> section in index.html to change colors (e.g., button color from #ff6600 to your brand color).
Add More Sections: Extend the HTML to include additional elements like navigation or footer.
Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
